1
00:00:06,150 --> 00:00:09,420
♪By the small window♪

2
00:00:10,070 --> 00:00:13,260
♪She is grooming herself♪

3
00:00:13,580 --> 00:00:19,860
♪A fleeting dream at night
brings me back home♪

4
00:00:20,100 --> 00:00:22,180
♪Through willows glows the sinking sun♪

5
00:00:22,300 --> 00:00:23,980
♪Over walls so still and bare♪

6
00:00:24,140 --> 00:00:26,900
♪A few faint strokes remain,
shadows of words♪

7
00:00:27,100 --> 00:00:33,500
♪In my twilight years,
I yearn for what is lost♪

8
00:00:33,540 --> 00:00:36,420
♪I try not to remember♪

9
00:00:36,460 --> 00:00:40,620
♪How far we were apart♪

10
00:00:40,820 --> 00:00:47,620
♪But forgetting is hard, with nowhere
to talk my cold thoughts out♪

11
00:00:47,860 --> 00:00:54,740
♪We looked at each other, silent,
lines of tears coursing down♪

12
00:00:54,860 --> 00:00:59,100
♪Now I gaze alone at the full moon,
entranced by its wistful beauty♪

13
00:00:59,100 --> 00:01:02,980
[Agarwood Like a Dream]

14
00:01:03,140 --> 00:01:07,180
[Episode 19]

15
00:01:07,900 --> 00:01:09,540
It's a difficult time for the Ye family.

16
00:01:10,260 --> 00:01:12,620
We don't have much silver left
for everyone.

17
00:01:13,340 --> 00:01:16,340
Yet, we mean goodwill.

18
00:01:17,300 --> 00:01:18,700
I hope you can accept it.

19
00:01:18,820 --> 00:01:20,500
You haven't managed
the pavilion for long,

20
00:01:20,860 --> 00:01:22,820
but you've treated us kindly.

21
00:01:22,820 --> 00:01:24,540
We would like to follow you.

22
00:01:24,780 --> 00:01:26,100
Yes, we don't want to go.

23
00:01:26,820 --> 00:01:27,820
Why stay here?

24
00:01:28,020 --> 00:01:28,940
Do you want to starve?

25
00:01:32,100 --> 00:01:33,500
You all have families.

26
00:01:34,340 --> 00:01:35,540
Take the silver

27
00:01:36,500 --> 00:01:38,340
and find a decent job.

28
00:01:56,820 --> 00:01:57,620
Take it.

29
00:01:58,100 --> 00:01:58,940
Don't worry.

30
00:01:59,700 --> 00:02:01,540
My mother left me a house.

31
00:02:02,260 --> 00:02:04,140
Grandmother and I can stay there.

32
00:02:21,260 --> 00:02:22,420
Take this.

33
00:02:24,740 --> 00:02:25,700
I'm not leaving.

34
00:02:26,260 --> 00:02:28,700
You saved my life.

35
00:02:29,260 --> 00:02:30,060
I am your maid

36
00:02:30,420 --> 00:02:32,260
all this life.

37
00:02:32,260 --> 00:02:34,460
I've always appreciated your gratitude.

38
00:02:35,820 --> 00:02:37,020
Don't worry about me.

39
00:02:38,340 --> 00:02:39,140
Go.

40
00:02:47,260 --> 00:02:48,260
Go.

41
00:02:51,020 --> 00:02:52,260
All of you, leave.

42
00:04:03,620 --> 00:04:04,420
Mind the heat.

43
00:04:04,900 --> 00:04:05,740
Let me do it.

44
00:04:19,860 --> 00:04:20,700
Let me do it.

45
00:04:24,700 --> 00:04:26,260
Why is your hand so cold?

46
00:04:27,940 --> 00:04:30,900
Perhaps it got cold in the snow.

47
00:04:32,340 --> 00:04:33,940
The Ye family has collapsed.

48
00:04:36,020 --> 00:04:38,860
Perhaps I can take care of you.

49
00:04:42,580 --> 00:04:43,380
Meng.

50
00:04:47,060 --> 00:04:48,500
I don't know when it started,

51
00:04:48,500 --> 00:04:50,220
but you've been in my heart.

52
00:04:51,340 --> 00:04:52,380
Mr. Nan Qing,

53
00:04:52,900 --> 00:04:54,820
I've always considered you
as a dear friend.

54
00:04:55,140 --> 00:04:56,060
That has never changed.

55
00:05:06,340 --> 00:05:09,500
Madam Ye must have caught
the winter chill.

56
00:05:10,740 --> 00:05:11,740
But don't worry.

57
00:05:12,060 --> 00:05:13,620
As long as you agree to be with me,

58
00:05:13,620 --> 00:05:15,060
I will treat her as my grandmother.

59
00:05:15,460 --> 00:05:17,700
I will provide the best medicine
for her treatment.

60
00:05:23,980 --> 00:05:25,940
But I've had someone in my heart.

61
00:05:27,660 --> 00:05:29,340
There's no space for anyone else.

62
00:05:29,500 --> 00:05:31,220
Ye Buhan has died.

63
00:05:31,660 --> 00:05:33,500
How can you not forget a dead person?

64
00:05:46,340 --> 00:05:48,100
Lots have happened recently.

65
00:05:48,860 --> 00:05:50,100
It keeps me thinking,

66
00:05:51,140 --> 00:05:52,580
was our encounter

67
00:05:52,980 --> 00:05:54,340
a coincidence

68
00:05:55,580 --> 00:05:56,980
or was there something behind it?

69
00:06:02,660 --> 00:06:03,500
Bai...

70
00:06:03,500 --> 00:06:04,500
Cheng...

71
00:06:04,500 --> 00:06:05,500
Zhi.

72
00:06:15,540 --> 00:06:16,340
Meng.

73
00:06:17,700 --> 00:06:18,780
If you wish,

74
00:06:20,180 --> 00:06:22,180
I'm willing to always be your Nan Qing.

75
00:06:24,980 --> 00:06:26,700
One can cover their face

76
00:06:26,980 --> 00:06:28,420
and change their voice.

77
00:06:29,380 --> 00:06:31,420
But the scent of Bai Chengzhi on you

78
00:06:32,500 --> 00:06:34,380
is something I will never forget.

79
00:06:35,180 --> 00:06:36,940
Madam Ye is not dead yet.

80
00:06:38,820 --> 00:06:41,500
I will find the best medicine
to treat her.

81
00:06:43,140 --> 00:06:45,980
My family has controlled
the medicine business in Shangjing.

82
00:06:46,340 --> 00:06:47,460
Just say the word...

83
00:06:49,940 --> 00:06:51,540
Meng...

84
00:06:57,780 --> 00:06:58,900
If you'll excuse me.

85
00:07:00,580 --> 00:07:01,540
Three days later,

86
00:07:01,940 --> 00:07:04,380
if you arrive at my place
in your bridal sedan,

87
00:07:05,300 --> 00:07:06,940
I will take over

88
00:07:07,620 --> 00:07:08,900
the Ye family business with you.

89
00:07:21,810 --> 00:07:24,120
[Ye's Mansion]

90
00:07:24,610 --> 00:07:26,710
[Bai's Mansion]

91
00:07:27,340 --> 00:07:28,940
If the Qixiang Pavilion
really closes down,

92
00:07:28,940 --> 00:07:30,940
Shangjing's five prestigious merchants
will be reduced to four.

93
00:07:30,940 --> 00:07:32,540
Thank you for taking over the pavilion.

94
00:07:32,540 --> 00:07:35,780
The Bai family will replace
the Ye family in the top five.

95
00:07:36,060 --> 00:07:38,900
Seems we underestimated the Bai family.

96
00:07:39,100 --> 00:07:42,060
You're the leading medicinal supplier
in Shangjing.

97
00:07:42,500 --> 00:07:44,460
Medicine is meant to save people.

98
00:07:44,460 --> 00:07:48,260
You're now saving
the Qixiang Pavilion's century-old legacy.

99
00:07:49,140 --> 00:07:51,420
I didn't expect
the master of the Bai family

100
00:07:51,420 --> 00:07:53,140
to be Mr. Nan Qing,

101
00:07:53,140 --> 00:07:55,500
an elegant gentleman.

102
00:07:56,340 --> 00:07:57,900
What a truly talented

103
00:07:57,900 --> 00:07:58,940
and modest young man.

104
00:08:01,980 --> 00:08:03,220
Thank you all for your support.

105
00:08:03,860 --> 00:08:07,180
Congratulations, Mr. Bai,
on taking over the Qixiang Pavilion.

106
00:08:07,260 --> 00:08:08,060
Please.

107
00:08:11,290 --> 00:08:14,930
[Ye's Mansion]

108
00:08:16,860 --> 00:08:17,660
A bridal sedan?

109
00:08:17,700 --> 00:08:18,740
A bridal sedan?

110
00:08:51,700 --> 00:08:52,460
Meng.

111
00:08:54,180 --> 00:08:55,340
I'm glad you came.

112
00:08:55,940 --> 00:08:57,260
I knew on that day,

113
00:08:58,260 --> 00:08:59,660
the one that wanted me dead

114
00:08:59,660 --> 00:09:01,060
was Bai Chengzhi.

115
00:09:02,860 --> 00:09:04,260
The one who let me go

116
00:09:04,260 --> 00:09:05,820
was Nan Qing.

117
00:09:06,780 --> 00:09:07,580
Don't worry.

118
00:09:08,740 --> 00:09:09,380
From now on,

119
00:09:10,260 --> 00:09:11,940
I am Nan Qing, yours alone.

120
00:09:15,340 --> 00:09:16,660
It is now the auspicious hour.

121
00:09:18,300 --> 00:09:20,020
First, bow to heaven and earth.

122
00:09:25,300 --> 00:09:26,820
Second, bow to your parents.

123
00:09:30,620 --> 00:09:32,180
Husband and wife, bow to each other.

124
00:09:38,260 --> 00:09:39,900
You really think I'm dead?

125
00:09:41,580 --> 00:09:42,740
Mr. Ye!

126
00:10:22,420 --> 00:10:25,300
♪Familiar yet strange sights♪

127
00:10:25,820 --> 00:10:28,220
♪The tale's first light♪

128
00:10:28,820 --> 00:10:30,620
♪Growing with time's flow♪

129
00:10:31,020 --> 00:10:34,140
♪Somber and mournful grief♪

130
00:10:34,540 --> 00:10:37,420
♪The final act, my swan song as a bait♪

131
00:10:37,740 --> 00:10:40,460
♪Has freed the heart from all desires♪

132
00:10:41,140 --> 00:10:45,460
♪As I dance with wolves,
love lies hidden deep♪

133
00:10:47,780 --> 00:10:52,340
♪The scented sachet,
a memory that never fades♪

134
00:10:53,100 --> 00:10:57,540
♪With every passing day,
our love simmers and ignites♪

135
00:10:58,820 --> 00:11:01,700
♪The ache born
from our ephemeral meetings♪

136
00:11:02,300 --> 00:11:05,100
♪Etched upon the canvas of my heart♪

137
00:11:05,740 --> 00:11:10,140
♪How to untangle
this lasting, aching desire♪

138
00:11:12,020 --> 00:11:14,500
♪In the face of such a bewitching gaze?♪

139
00:11:15,380 --> 00:11:20,900
♪Soft melodies caress locked windows,
reaching out to the setting sun♪

140
00:11:21,820 --> 00:11:24,340
♪Gently adorning with twilight's charm♪

141
00:11:24,700 --> 00:11:27,340
♪My remaining breaths,
the thoughts that they bear♪

142
00:11:27,860 --> 00:11:32,340
♪The vision of you,
the one that fills my mind♪
